Package com.github.robtimus.checkstyle.checks

Contains additional Checkstyle checks.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LicenseCommentCheck
    Checks whether or not a Java source file has a valid leading license comment.
    NoBlankLineAfterSymbolsCheck
    Checks that files do not contain blank lines after lines that only consist of specific symbols.
    NoBlankLineBeforeSymbolsCheck
    Checks that files do not contain blank lines before lines that only consist of specific symbols.
    NoSubsequentBlankLinesCheck
    Checks that files do not have multiple blank lines in a row.
    NoTrailingWhitespaceCheck
    Checks that files have no trailing whitespace.
